title: Star Wars: The Deadly Hunter
description: Nobody knows her name. Nobody knows when she will strike. All they know is that she is a deadly bounty hunter--and her latest mission has taken her to Coruscant, home of the Jedi.Her target: an old friend of Qui-Gon Jinn's.Qui-Gon and his apprentice, Obi-Wan Kenobi, make an attempt to catch her...and fail.Now they are her targets, too.
author: Jude Watson
